{
  "page": "Galazza Galare",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/50px-Meereen.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/75px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/100px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Galazza Galare</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/50px-Meereen.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/75px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/100px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Galazza_Galare,_the_Green_Grace1.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Galazza Galare, the Green Grace1.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Galazza_Galare%2C_the_Green_Grace1.jpg/350px-Galazza_Galare%2C_the_Green_Grace1.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"/images/e/e7/Galazza_Galare%2C_the_Green_Grace1.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Galazza Galare, the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a>, by Sasha Gladysh ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Galare\" title=\"House of Galare\">House of Galare</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Graces\" title=\"Graces\">Graces</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nIn or before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_217_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">217&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgalazza_galare.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgalazza_galare.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Galazza Galare</b> is the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a>, the high priestess of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">Temple of the Graces</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> She is from the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Galare\" title=\"House of Galare\">House of Galare</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Galazza\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Galazza</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Galazza\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Galazza</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Category:Images of Galazza Galare\">Images of Galazza Galare</a></div>\n<p>Galazza is a tall, graceful-looking woman, despite being past eighty years old. Her hair is white and her skin parchment thin, but the years have not dimmed her piercing green eyes. <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> thinks they are sad eyes, full of wisdom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a>, Galazza Galare wears a shimmering green silk veil that covers her whole face, except for her eyes. She has a soft and kindly voice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Galazza's counsel proves invaluable to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_Meereen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen of Meereen\">Queen of Meereen</a>, as she is a voice for peace and tolerance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Two of Galazza's cousins, <a href=\"/index.php/Grazhar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grazhar\">Grazhar</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Qezza\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qezza\">Qezza</a>, are made the queen's <a href=\"/index.php/Cupbearers_of_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Cupbearers of Daenerys Targaryen\">cupbearers and hostages</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The Green Grace is accompanied by a dozen <a href=\"/index.php/White_Graces\" title=\"White Graces\">White Graces</a> when she arrives at the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Pyramid\" title=\"Great Pyramid\">Great Pyramid</a> for a private supper with the queen. Galazza suggests Daenerys marry <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a> to achieve the peace she desires.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Three <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Graces\" title=\"Blue Graces\">Blue Graces</a> accompany the Green Grace to inform Daenerys about a rider bringing <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_flux\" title=\"Bloody flux\">disease</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Astapor\" title=\"Siege of Astapor\">Astapor</a> to Meereen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While discussing Daenerys's upcoming wedding to Hizdahr, the Green Grace says that the queen should re-open the <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_pits_of_Meereen\" title=\"Fighting pits of Meereen\">fighting pits of Meereen</a>, which would be pleasing to the gods.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> On the day of <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Hizdahr_zo_Loraq_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Hizdahr zo Loraq and Daenerys Targaryen\">the wedding</a>, Galazza and her fellow <a href=\"/index.php/Graces\" title=\"Graces\">Graces</a> wait for the bride and groom outside their temple.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Galazza and many of her Graces attend the reopening of <a href=\"/index.php/Daznak%27s_Pit\" title=\"Daznak&#39;s Pit\">Daznak's Pit</a>, but Daenerys disappears from the pit on <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Queensguard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Queensguard\">Lord Commander of the Queensguard</a>, seizes control of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> in his queen's absence, and he sends Galazza to the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai%27i\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yunkai&#39;i\">Yunkai'i</a> to offer his peace terms and gold for the three hostages held by the Yunkai'i. <a href=\"/index.php/Skahaz_mo_Kandaq\" title=\"Skahaz mo Kandaq\">Skahaz mo Kandaq</a> distrusts Galazza.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Galaza returns to inform Barristan that the Yunkai'i have refused his offer, and that the only price they will accept is the death of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>. She tells him that Daenerys is dead, and that he should let her dragons die as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Galazza\">Quotes by Galazza</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Galazza\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/300px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/450px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/600px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Green Grace, by Naomimakesart ©</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The Mother of Dragons must don the <a href=\"/index.php/Tokar\" title=\"Tokar\">tokar</a> or be forever hated. In the wools of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> or a gown of <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myrish</a> lace, Your Radiance shall forever remain a stranger amongst us, a grotesque outlander, a barbarian conqueror. <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>'s queen must be a lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Ghis\" title=\"Old Ghis\">Old Ghis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Galazza to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I shall return to the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">Temple of the Graces</a> and pray for the gods to show my queen the course of wisdom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Galazza to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The peace that we worked so hard to forge flutters like a leaf in an autumn wind. These are dire days.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Galazza to <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Galazza\">Quotes about Galazza</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Galazza\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_zo_Galare\" title=\"Grazdan zo Galare\">Grazdan</a>, she had been forewarned, was a cousin of the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a>, whose support she had found invaluable. The priestess was a voice for peace, acceptance, and obedience to lawful authority.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a> will accomplish nothing. She may be conspiring with the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>'i even as we sit here.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Skahaz_mo_Kandaq\" title=\"Skahaz mo Kandaq\">Skahaz mo Kandaq</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Galazza Galare was attended by four <a href=\"/index.php/Pink_Graces\" title=\"Pink Graces\">Pink Graces</a>. An aura of wisdom and dignity seemed to surround her that Ser Barristan could not help but admire. This is a strong woman, and she has been a faithful friend to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galazza_Galare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Galazza Galare</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafgalazza_galare.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgalazza_galare.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Galazza Galare.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">4.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\">6.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</